snippet.description:
Witness the love with Chaleya, presenting the second song from the highly-awaited film Jawan directed by Atlee. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on 7th September 2023 in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

snippet.title: 200 Pounds BIG TUNA FISH | Tuna Fish Cutting and Cooking in Village | Tuna Fish Steak Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook big Tuna fish to make fish steak recipe. In this video, we show how we cutting the giant tuna for cooking. After cooking Tuna fish meat, the fish bones and head are cooked separately by making fish curry.

Finally, we eat in the evening. The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: Every Girls School On Independence Day | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This video shows what happens in every girls school on Independence day. Scenarios like going on shopping with Indian mom to fancy dress shop , singing lessons for 15th august function in school , singing vande matram , choir selection of students , dance practices and coping up with syllabus , science teacher , other subject mam scolding and pissed off with students for missing their periods ,  dancing on desh rangila , dressing up for school function putting makeup , lots of red lipstick , rented jewellery , gudda , making bun , dressing up as different states punjab , gujrat , kashmir , west bangal , kolkata , assam , maharashtra , marathi , tamil , kanayakumari , chennia , school dance competition , making vlog in school , disscusing which class performed the best , hooting for our friends , class party on independence day bringing homemade food our cooks for us pao bhaji , cheese sandwiches , speaking on stage on democratic india , secular india , decorating class , cutting glaze paper , making chart paper on freedom fighters , rani laxmi baxi , jhansi ki rani , bhagat singh , gandhi ji , tricolor balloon decoration , making indian flag , indian mom arranging artificial jewellery for daughters school fancy dress , sewing her dress for proper fitting , maa vs beti , maa beti , our favs chinky and savitri , Patang baazi , Getting together on friend's terrace , beer bottles, Instagram photos with Indian flag , Girls doing Tricolour Eye makeup looks , School functions, 15 august dance practice in school, School life and choir singing on desh bhakhti songs , Fancy dress shopping for like Jhansi Ki Rani Mahatma Gandhi ji , Bhagat singh , freedom fighters , Getting laddoos , munch chocolate in School snacks , middle class family watching parade on Tv , forwarding Whatsapp messages of Swatantra Diwas going out for watching movie and so much more.. 
You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days .
Relive and Relish your School life.. These are the best days of school
Do share it with your friends , family , teachers , mothers , dost especially with school ones.. 
Happy Independence Day Everyone 🇮🇳

snippet.title: Independence Day: PM Modi ने लाल किला से देशवासियों को स्वतंत्रता दिवस के अपने Speech में क्या बोला?
snippet.description:
PM Modi Speech On Independence Day 2023: प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी ने 77वें स्वतंत्रता दिवस पर लाल किले की प्राचीर पर झंडा फहराया. पीएम मोदी ने 10वीं बार लाल किले पर राष्ट्र ध्वज फहराया है. इसके बाद पीएम मोदी ने देशवासियों को संबोधित किया. अपने संबोधन में पीएम ने देशवासियों शब्द की जगह परिवारजन शब्द का इस्तेमाल किया. इसके साथ ही उन्होंने विकसित राष्ट्र के संकल्प को दोहराया. इसके साथ ही उन्होंने मणिपुर, युवा, नारी शक्ति सहित नए वर्ल्ड ऑर्डर पर अपनी बात रखी.

Prime Minister Narendra Modi hoisted the flag on the ramparts of the Red Fort on the 77th Independence Day. PM Modi has hoisted the national flag at the Red Fort for the 10th time. After this PM Modi addressed the countrymen. In his address, the PM used the word family instead of the word countrymen. Along with this, he reiterated the resolve of a developed nation. Along with this, he spoke on new world order including Manipur, youth, women power.

#independenceday #pmmodi #pmmodispeech

snippet.title: Independence Day 2023: PM Modi hoists National Flag at iconic Red Fort
snippet.description:
The nation echoes with zeal and enthusiasm on the occasion of 77th Independence Day. Prime Minister Narendra Modi arrived at Red Fort for Independence Day celebrations. Upon his arrival, he was received by Defence Minister Rajnath Singh, MoS Defence Ajay Bhatt. Indian Prime Minister inspected Guard of Honour at iconic Red Fort on 77th I-Day. PM Modi hoisted the National flag at the ramparts of the historic monument. He will deliver the customary address to the nation from the Red Fort. This year’s Independence Day will culminate the ‘Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav’ celebrations.  

#IndependenceDay2023 #NationalFlag #NarendraModi

snippet.title: Easily 3 Star Clashiversary Challenge #3 (Clash of Clans)
snippet.description:
The Clash of Clans 2023 Clashiversary Event progresses to Challenge 3. The Future Queen Skin is showcased in this level designed by Yuta14. It involves a Queen Charge strategy to the Town Hall and can be tricky if you have not done it before. I did want to thank iTzu for helping me with the consistency of this method - namely how to save all of the troops until after the TH is destroyed. If you activate it too early it can end up taking down your healers. Best of luck with your 3 stars!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3851 | 16 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3851: Saare Bhartiya Bhai Bhai
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide notifies Champaklal that Tapu Sena has now consented to make preparations for the Gokuldham Society's Independence Day event. Champaklal counsels Bhide on how to cope with the new generation of children, and Bhide decides to follow Champaklal's advice. Babita and Iyer are surprised to discover the spectacular decor at Gokuldham the next morning, and they admire Tapu Sena's work. Everyone celebrates Tapu Sena's piece of art, yet it quickly vanishes. Bhide becomes enraged once more and decides to begin the flag-raising ceremony without them. So, where has Tapu Sena gone?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3851, 16 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: 1 कप पोहा से 10 मिनट में बनाए खस्ता कुरकुरा नाश्ता जो पूरे 2 महीने तक खाए /Masala papdi
snippet.description:
Siri Rs 20 /- mein tayyar karein 1/2 kg Masala Papdi…1 Cup Pohe se Sirf 10 minute mein ban jata hai…aur pure 2 marine ise kha saktein …ekdum kasta kurkura nashta hai…jisse aap sham ke shamay garma-garm Chai ke sath khaye …Khasta Nashta…Store upto 2 months …Tea time Snacks…Masala Papdi

Ingredients
1. Flattened Rice  1 Cup
2. Gram Flour 1/2 Cup
3. Water 1 tbsp
4. Refined Oil 1 tsp
5. Cumin Seeds 1/2 tsp
6. Asafoetida 1/4 tsp
7. Turmeric Powder 1/4 tsp
8. Red Chilli Flakes 1 tsp
9. Black Sesame Seeds 1 tsp
10. Coriander Leaves 1/4 Cup
11. Garam Masala 1/4 tsp
12. Dry Mango Powder 1/2 tsp
13. Salt as per taste

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 15th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: ये देश है वीर जवानों का | Independence Day Special Desh Bhakti Song 2023 | Best Desh Bhakti Geet
snippet.description:
ये देश है वीर जवानों का अलबेलों का मस्तानों का | Independence Day Special 2023 | Desh Bhakti Geet 
------
Song: Yeh Desh Hai Veer Jawanon Ka
Movie: Naya Daur
Singer: Mohammed Rafi, Balbir
Music Director: O.P. Nayyar
Film Star: Dilip Kumar, Vyjayanthimala, Ajeet, Chand Usmani, Nazir Hussain, Leela Chitnis, Johnny Walker
Director: B.R. Chopra,
Lyricist: Sahir Ludhianvi
------
Lyrics:
o ye desh hai veer jawano ka
albelo ka mastano ka
is desh ka yaaro hoy
is desh ka yaaro kya kahna
ye desh hai duniya ka gahna

o yaha chaudi chaati veero ki
yaha bholi shakle heero ki
yaha gaate hai raanjhe hoy
yaha gaate hai raanjhe masti me
masti hai jhume basti me

o pedo pe bahare jhulo ki
raaho me kataare phulo ki
yaha hasta hai saawan hoy
yaha hasta hai saawan baalo me
khilti hai kaliya gaalo me

o kahi dangal surkh jawano ke
kahi kartab teer kamano ke
yaha nit nit mele hoy
yaha nit nit mele sajte hai
nit dhol aur tashe bajte hai

o dilbar ke liye dildaar hai ham
dushman ke liye talwar hai ham
maindaan me agar ham
maindaan me agar ham dat jaaye

#देशभक्तिगीत #deshbhaktisongs #deshbhaktigeet #15aug2023 #स्वतंत्रतादिवस

snippet.description:
പുതിയ തന്ത്രങ്ങളുമായി ബാലു. കൂട്ടിന് രാം കുമാറും. ഉപ്പും മുളകും വീട്ടിൽ ഇനി സംഭവിക്കുന്നത് കാത്തിരുന്ന് കാണാം...


'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?

#UppumMulakum2

Sirf Tum Episode 35 Teaser - 16th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 32 Teaser - 15th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 32 Teaser - 15th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya

Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela

Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3850 | 15 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3850: Bhide VS Tapu Sena
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide discusses Independence Day with the students he tutors and asks them to visit the school mandatory on the occasion of 15 August. Later, Tapu Sena begs Bhide if they may skip the big Independence Day celebration and instead take a picnic to Khandala with their college mates. Bhide refuses to allow the children for the picnic to which they announce an open rebellion. Bhide visits Jetha's place and meets Bapuji and asks Bhide to give the children a lesson. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3850, 15 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2│Flowers│EP# 313
snippet.description:
അമ്മമാരില്ലാത്ത വീട്ടിൽ അച്ഛന്മാരുടെ വിളയാട്ടം!! പക്ഷെ കുട്ടിപ്പട്ടാളത്തോട് പിടിച്ചുനിൽക്കാൻ അത്ര എളുപ്പമായിരിക്കില്ല. ഉപ്പും മുളകും വീട്ടിൽ ഇനി എന്തുനടക്കുമെന്ന് കണ്ടറിഞ്ഞ് കാണാം... 

'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?



#uppummulakum  ​#BijuSopanam #NishaSarang

This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?



#uppummulakum  ​#BijuSopanam #NishaSarang

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

The electricity suddenly went off from Gokuldham. Everything was all set up to watch Tapu Sena's advertisement. Daya calls Sundar. Jetha tells her that all this has happened because of him only. Everyone finally watch Tapu Sena's advertisement. They praised their kids. Watch the full episode to know more.

Episode - 265
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

Nattu Kaka and Bagha call Jetha to inform him that money has been taken in their hamlet and they require assistance. snippet.description:

What gives a sitting Prime Minister (with 10 years of incumbency) so much confidence ???? Hubris or the deep understanding of electoral maths and the knowledge that the 26 allies of I.N.D.I.A - will never work out a proper seat sharing arrangement? In this deep dive - we take the most indepth look at the numbers - and see just how many can I.N.D.I.A win - and why Congress is still the weakest link.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu ||Something Missamma Episode 06 || Pre Wedding || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Episode 06 Pre Wedding MCM
Filmymoji releases its new episode of Missamma series where Middle class Madhu will be forced to assist Penta Reddy in chopping someone’s hand off. Meanwhile Dupesh lands in jammalamadugu and proposes to take a pre-wedding shoot of bulli Guvva and Sravani. The broker introduces the alliance as a Dubai return and Madhu blackmails him for money for not revealing this narrative. Dupesh takes out bride and the groom along with MCM and Komali for the pre-wedding shoot and instead of taking pictures he convinces bulli Guvva to click his pictures with the bride. Watch the full episode to find out the shocking truth which Dupesh reveals about the marriage and whether NaatuGuntala gang finds out about the whereabouts of Madhu.

Meanwhile Dupesh lands in jammalamadugu and proposes to take a pre-wedding shoot of bulli Guvva and Sravani. The broker introduces the alliance as a Dubai return and Madhu blackmails him for money for not revealing this narrative. Dupesh takes out bride and the groom along with MCM and Komali for the pre-wedding shoot and instead of taking pictures he convinces bulli Guvva to click his pictures with the bride. Watch the full episode to find out the shocking truth which Dupesh reveals about the marriage and whether NaatuGuntala gang finds out about the whereabouts of Madhu.

Thimiru  is a 2006 Indian Tamil-language action film written and directed by Tarun Gopi in his directorial debut. It stars Vishal, Reema Sen, Sriya Reddy, I. M. Vijayan, Manoj K. Jayan and Vadivelu, while Kiran Rathod makes a cameo appearance. The film's score and soundtrack are composed by Yuvan Shankar Raja. Produced by Vikram Krishna, under the banner of G K Film Corporation, Thimiru was released on 4 August 2006 and became one of the top-grossing Tamil films in 2006.

snippet.description:
Vijay Deverakonda & Samantha Mesmerizing Dance At KUSHI Musical Concert on Mythri Movie Makers.

Kushi 2023 Latest Movie Ft. Vijay Deverakonda and Samantha in lead roles. The film was Written and Directed by Shiva Nirvana. snippet.title: Chandrayaan-3 Reveals Latest Images of MOON | Latest Update of Chandrayaan 3
snippet.description:
Description - Hello Getsetflyers Gaurav here… And this is the latest update for Chandrayaan-3. At the stroke of midnight of 1st August, Chandrayaan-3 has successfully left the Earth’s gravitational field and now is heading towards the moon with full force. Also, I will be discussing what exactly happened till now about Chandrayaan-3 right from its hours before launch. So, tune into this video to get the entire coverage.
